<L><PB N="114" REF="021826_0113_0FB5C0416B4E9410">
Her&s;elf; while con&s;cious of her high de&s;cent,</L>
<L>She longs and labours to embrace her <HI>Sire;</HI></L>
<L>Embracing, in an ocean of delight,</L>
