<LG>
<L>Enamour'd with my theme, on flaming wings</L>
<L>Above th' Aonian or Parna&s;&s;ian mount</L>
<L>I &s;oar, as emulous to reach tho&s;e &s;weet</L>
<L>And everla&s;ting lays which fill all Heav'n</L>
<L>With melody beyond containment full,</L>
<L>Bounds o'er her walls, and &s;preading far and wide,</L>
<L>Echoes from &s;tar to &s;tar, from &s;phere to &s;phere;</L>
<L>The pure ethereal wafts the balmy found</L>
<L>Thro' infinites of &s;pace.&mdash;</L>
<L>Mounting, I meet the dulcet harmony,</L>
