<L>Turn &s;hort; into <HI>thy&s;elf</HI> de&s;cend, and &s;eek</L>
<L><PB N="116" REF="021826_0115_0FB5C04949233BC0">
For plea&s;ure <HI>there,</HI> and in thy God, thy life;</L>
