<L><PB N="117" REF="021826_0116_0FB5C04CB695C528">
<HI>One</HI> plea&s;ing act of virtue to the &s;oul</L>
<L>More joy affords, than all the plea&s;ures vice</L>
<L>Can boa&s;t. The &s;ecret &s;eeds of con&s;tant, pure</L>
<L>Delight, are &s;own in virtuous minds, by deeds</L>
