<L>Give <HI>la&s;ting</HI> joys to that which <HI>never fades?</HI></L>
<L><PB N="119" REF="021826_0118_0FB5C0506172ED60">
Now on <HI>Religion</HI> look:&mdash;a&s;k you (with &s;miles</L>
<L>That &s;peak your &s;corn) what joys from her? a&s;k then</L>
<L>What is't to be religious? 'tis to <HI>feel</HI></L>
<L>As <HI>angels feel,</HI> when they &s;urround the throne</L>
<L>Of the <HI>Eternal,</HI> radiant circles form,</L>
